text:
As we wrap up rehearsals, would you mind
sharing your thoughts with the camera?

To everyone watching the video!
Hello!

I'm Chiyoko Sonoda from HO-KA-GO CLIMAX GIRLS,
the chocolate idol!

We've just finished rehearsals for the upcoming
live event with all the 283PRO idols...
And it's shaping up to be absolutely fantastic!

I promise we'll make sure everyone has a
great time, so please look forward to it!
